\c 120 Munyengetero womunhu ari pakutambudzika Rwiyo rworwendo. 120 1 Pakutambudzika kwangu ndakadana kuna Jehovha, Iye akandipindura. 2 Rwirai mweya wangu, Jehovha, pamiromo inoreva nhema, Naparurimi runonyengedzera. 3 Iwe uchapiweiko, chinyi chichawedzerwa kwauri, Iwe rurimi runonyengedzera? 4 Miseve inopinza yeanesimba, Namazimbe anopfuta omurara. 5 Ndine ropa rakaipa zvandiri mutorwa paMesheki, Zvandigere pamatende eKedhari!
